/*
 * Author: commy2
 * Check if the unit can interact.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: The player. <OBJECT>
 * 1: The interaction target. objNull to ignore. <OBJECT>
 * 2: Exceptions. What general conditions are to skip? (default: []) <ARRAY>
 *
