/*
 * Author: commy2, Jonpas
 * Fixes position of an object. E.g. moves object above ground and adjusts to terrain slope. Requires local object.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * Object <OBJECT>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * None
 *
 * Example:
