/*
 * Author: esteldunedain
 * Return action point from path
 * Note: This function is NOT global.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: List of Action Tree <ARRAY>
 * 1: Path <ARRAY>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * Action node <ARRAY> or <NIL> if not found 
 *
 * Example:
