/*
 * Author: GitHawk
 * Get the remaining ammunition amount.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: Ammo Truck <OBJECT>
 * 1: Unit <OBJECT>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * None
 *
 * Example:
