 * Gets the bore height of the currently used weapon & optic combination
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: Unit <OBJECT>
 * 1: Weapon index <NUMBER>
 * 2: Weapon <CLASS>
 * 3: Optic <CLASS>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * bore height <NUMBER>
