/*
 * Author: SilentSpike
 * Function used to get an appropriate icon for provided group. Approximate.
 *
 * Arguments:
 * 0: Group to get the icon of <GROUP>
 * 1: Return icons for draw3D use <BOOL> (Default: false)
 *
 * Return Value:
 * Icon of group <STRING>
 *
